<p>Delete <code>site.js</code> and try it!</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">gulp</div></code></pre>
<p>On hey, welcome back <code>site.js</code>. Now when you need a page-specific JavaScript
file, just add another <code>addScript</code> call here. Feeling powerful?</p>
<p>What else can you do? Well, if you're into CoffeeScript, you can grab a plugin
for that and mix it right in. Do whatever you want.</p>

    
